Definition: distribute according to a plan or set apart for a special purpose
Example: I am allocating a loaf of bread to everyone on a daily basis; I'm allocating the rations for the camping trip
Synonyms: adj, all, distributive, allocatable, allocable, noun, act, allocation, possession, person, allocator, apportion, apportionable, apportionment, assign, distribute, according, to, a, plan, or, set, apart, for, special, purpose, I, am, allocating, loaf, of, bread, everyone, on, daily, basis, m, the, rations, camping, trip
Frame: 8,15
Category: verb.possession
